{"tid":85765,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]遊客不聽勸闖未開發景點　遭落石砸中身亡","createTime":"2017-01-18T14:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T17:56:47.000Z","uid":32407,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f384551ce7df1cfc5473aea6f499dbf9f623609a","tid":85765,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=pWbpC%2BUQwT7NA%2FgVgW1ez38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=5c100f27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 四川都江堰市龍池景區地質災害頻發，屬於未開發景點，由於該處危機四伏，因此通往景區山門差不多每隔1公里便設有警示牌。然而總有一些人漠視安全、懶理警告，最終付上無可挽回的沉重代價。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，前日有30多名遊客不理勸告強行硬闖入山賞積雪，結果被困，其中一名遊客更慘遭落石砸中身亡。隨後消防員3次入山，先後將被困者救出。事發後，當地將設路障封閉進山通道，以免再有不幸事情發生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e5de3a6b309929ab9202788552c5ebf04097c9","tid":85765,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"抵呀！"},{"pid":"0af0e08b1be91305e53512ecfb4207f1571d8f19","tid":85765,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/ae/1560397_738346369520622_5816392467299671909_n.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140424043605\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fa%2Fae%2F1560397_738346369520622_5816392467299671909_n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140424043605&h=058a969b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"229dbc7c3d9e426e2f13f76e73f9f12bd70ee47b","tid":85765,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638b651ea854788825764651aec52e635c04417b","tid":85765,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20